params._v2Pid: The pool id of the dummy pool on the MCV2.

params._dummyToken: The address of the token to be deposited into MCV2.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._amount: Injection amount, the injection amount can be flexibly controlled.

depositForMasterChefV2Pool(address).notice: Deposits a dummy token to `MASTER_CHEF` MCV2. It will transfer all the `dummyToken` in the tx sender address.

withdraw(address).notice: Withdraw unexpected tokens sent to the receiver, can also withdraw cake.

documentation.text: @notice Harvest pending CAKE tokens from MasterChef V2.
